# =============================================================================
# üìù NOTES FOR DEVELOPERS
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. This file contains development-friendly defaults that work immediately
# 2. All secrets are weak and MUST be changed for production
# 3. Use 'docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d' for local development
# 4. Access the services at:
#    - Web Panel: http://localhost:3001
#    - API: http://localhost:3000
#    - MinIO Console: http://localhost:9001 (minioadmin/minioadmin)
#    - Karrio Dashboard: http://localhost:5001
#
# 5. To generate secure values for production:
#    - JWT_SECRET: openssl rand -hex 32
#    - ENCRYPTION_KEY: openssl rand -hex 16
#    - Other tokens: openssl rand -hex 32
#
# Happy coding! üöÄ